issues.body:
After double check on the following standards, 
- ITU-T L.1330
- ETSI ES 203 228 V1.4.1 (2022-04) 
- IEEE 802.3az-2003
I suggest to add the following definitions as mentioned in the above standards.
- power consumption; 
- energy consumption; 
- energy saving features; 
- energy-efficiency ethernet;
- site energy effciency;
If some of these terms are agreed to be added, I can provide a pull request for them, thanks.

